criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion criteria:

        • None

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  presence of neurological, vascular and musculoskeletal impairments at the lower and
             upper limbs level;

          -  being on pharmacological therapy related to either neural and/or vascular response,
             including hormonal contraceptives and oral supplements;

          -  being a current or former smoker;

          -  having an irregular menstrual cycle (26 to 35 days) up to three months before the
             beginning of the study,

          -  presenting contraindication for joint mobilization;

          -  being regularly involved in PS program.
